column24:
 just one that's ridiculously difficult to learn at start and where the high skill ceiling makes it pretty much impossible to play casually unless you restrict yourself to bot matches.

@EDIT: Tried a match after the Overdrive came out. Matchmaker still matched me and two other newbies against high-prestige players. Also just after one game I can tell Jimmy is insanely cheap with "lemme ambush and charge you into my turret halfway across the field while you can't even escape" tactics. There was a beta test for the new 'Nauts before that so there's no way they didn't catch that earlier.
